div.p:
—that you make a mid-April appearance at our Foreign Press Center here before
                        an invited list of (primarily European) journalists, and that the morality
                        theme figure prominently;

—that a chorus of European and American voices be raised—particularly from
                        those held in high regard in the FRG, which
                        is most sensitive to the unity issue;

—that a DOD/State/NSC/USICA group be formed this week to consider the most
                        effective observance of the 35th anniversary of V–E Day on May 9. There are indications that the USSR already has plans to use the observance
                        for political purposes;
